Package net.mattjw.okelydokuly

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArgParse
    Parse arguments for the Sudoku command line tool.
    ArgParse.Arguments
    Represents argument parsed for the command line tool.
    Grid
    This class represents a Sudoku grid throughout the solving process; i.e., from unsolved, to partially solved, to solved.
    Solver
    Solve Sudoku puzzles using a constraint-satisfcation backtracking search.
    SudokuIO
    Input and output of Sudoku grids.
    ValueSet
    This class tracks the possible remaining values a particular Sudoku cell may be assigned with; i.e., in CSP parlance, this is the domain of a cell.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidSudokuFileException
    Exception thrown if a Sudoku file has an invalid format.
    InvalidSudokuGridException
    Exception thrown if a Sudoku grid represented by a two-dimensional array is not valid.
    UnsolvedSudokuException
    Exception thrown if a Sudoku puzzle could not be solved by the solver; e.g., because the grid arrangement is invalid.
